'''Outer Kerner Way''' was a street in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]], [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. It split into [[Kerner Plaza/Legends|Kerner Plaza]] and [[Inner Curved Street/Legends|Inner Curved Street]].<ref name="Refresher 91">{{InsiderCite|91|Refresher Reading}}</ref>

[[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina]] was building number 3112 of this street.<ref name="Refresher 91" />

